! Wiener-Hopf方程

$$
\begin{aligned}
r_x(m)&=-\sum_{k=1}^p\alpha_kr_x(m-k)\quad m=1,2,\dots,p\\
\rho_{\rm{min}}&=r_x(0)+\sum_{k=1}^p\alpha_kr_x(k)
\end{aligned}
$$

